{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "马斯古拉 第3话 梦想中的和平之畔",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那么……接下来怎么办，\\n尤蒂尔？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这个嘛……虽然不知道\\n战斗人偶部队什么时候会来袭\\n会很危险，但我们必须前往圣树。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "白天尽量不休息来赶路吧。\\n但相应地，我们要在日落前\\n扎好营以防在夜间遭袭。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "好的，殿下。\\n眼看太阳快下山，赶紧找个\\n不易被袭击的地方扎营吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "我看看……有什么不容易\\n被战斗人偶发现的地方……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喔～只有这一带是平原啊。\\n虽然不太适合扎营，\\n但似乎便于掌握地形呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "同意。开始探索。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "说起来，我遇到卢卡\\n也是在一片很美的平原呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "说起来的确是。虽然当时\\n那里被狄涅尔帝国和战斗人偶夹击，\\n是个超级激战区就是了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "我还记得你在那里\\n不分敌我到处抢武器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "是啊。只要夺走战场上所有人的武器，\\n世上就不会再有斗争……\\n当时的我笃信这一点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我不在的期间，\\n你竟然做了那么没效率的事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "请不要过分责备我。\\n因为现在的我\\n跟你的看法相同。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "战场上只要存在祈愿和平、\\n关怀他人的心，便会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120151_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "战斗人偶Z",
            "context": "——再见、麦斯特罗。\\n你要、好好的……＂",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "催生自我的萌芽，\\n导致“生命”白白牺牲。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "所以我才决定战斗。\\n为了不再让任何人\\n像那样在我面前死去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是吗……但我觉得你的温柔\\n教会了我很多啊，只是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "既然你决定了，我就会支持你。\\n莱姬希，你也是吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "……\\n我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我……反对。\\n因为马斯古拉不战斗，\\n便等于是在战斗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "莱姬希……\\n这话是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "你所向往的和平的确不合实际，\\n但那也是这个时代的\\n大环境所导致的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "实际上，也有敌人曾受你的\\n思想行动感化而放下武器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "是啊……我曾无论对方怎么攻击\\n也决不还手，并坚持与其对话，\\n最终赢得了胜利呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "予以肯定。\\n你就是这样一路战斗过来的。\\n你过去的战斗方式，并没有错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "只要你继续坚持理想，\\n未来会有更多人类\\n理解你的战斗方式。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "你是要我坚持以理想示人吗？\\n可你过去一直说我软弱、\\n说我只会逃避战斗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我最初……觉得你有缺陷。\\n但是，现在我改变了想法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我的理想和你的理想都象征着\\n麦斯特罗所托付的和平……\\n我是这么认为的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "象征着麦斯特罗\\n所托付的和平？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "在不同的思想背景下寻求和平。\\n那就是我们的设计者——\\n麦斯特罗的愿望吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "我没有确切的证据。但是……\\n这是我内心的真实想法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "所以我不希望你拿起武器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "莱姬希……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "卢卡、莱姬希、马斯古拉！\\n太好了……总算找到你们了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是埃尔菲莉丝啊。\\n出什么事了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "嗯，我们遭到了刚才那支\\n战斗人偶部队的突袭！\\n你们快来支援！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "怎么可能！战斗人偶的维护\\n不可能在这么短的时间内完成。\\n怎么会这么快就再次来袭……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "虽然不知道敌人的情况……\\n但听起来很不妙。我们快走吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "马斯古拉，侦查完毕之后，\\n你先把自己的身体藏在附近。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "你只要在我体内\\n专心协助我就好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100045_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "莱姬希……我知道了！\\n那我们走吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100045_01_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}